{"tid":2000224,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"救命網際網路連線失敗，但是路由器的無線網路設定正常。","createTime":"2020-05-03T17:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T20:37:18.000Z","uid":258582,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41b9950edc605e52fd031a1157e31fc9dcdd145f","tid":2000224,"uid":258582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"各位巴打<br />\n啱啱搬咗新屋，寬頻公司用和記，本來都好地地，就早幾日阿女要網上學習所以攞咗部電腦返屋企俾佢用，我開機用電腦Wi-Fi連線就開始不斷咁斷線。<br />\n用部電腦直插上網速度好快好穩定，但係用返無線上網就不停咁斷線而家連手機都係咁。試過換幾隻router分別係華為Tp link 小米，直情攞唔到signal 。要用返本來嗰個tenda router 先至可以連到Wi-Fi連線，不過勁斷線。<br />\n<br />\n打電話上和記佢話佢哋嘅訊號完全冇問題，唔關佢公司事。<br />\n<br />\n求幫手"},{"pid":"d7d34f870155834f43df4d4b3331779ae8f0a186","tid":2000224,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傻記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"00bc390ff12ff1219be115fe0f0dd237d49a8d97","tid":2000224,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"咪撚用和記"},{"pid":"5ec7512383c06cf010ebc5b2ab16d50b66d122dd","tid":2000224,"uid":258582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7d34f870155834f43df4d4b3331779ae8f0a186","tid":2000224,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">傻記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:14:32.000Z","msg":"個屋苑得和記同Pccw揀，我貪平揀咗和記。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d5cd20081f7e989409b94ceb342c8f0eefbdfe","tid":2000224,"uid":258582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00bc390ff12ff1219be115fe0f0dd237d49a8d97","tid":2000224,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:10:19.000Z","msg":"咪撚用和記"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"新搬屋啱啱簽"},{"pid":